statements: SELECT token_id, amount, owner_address FROM token_ownership;
SELECT * FROM token_ownership WHERE amount > 100;
SELECT token_id, transaction_date, amount FROM token_transactions ORDER BY transaction_date DESC;
SELECT token_id, sender_address, receiver_address FROM token_transactions WHERE amount < 50;
SELECT * FROM token_transactions WHERE sender_address = '0x123456789';
SELECT * FROM token_ownership WHERE owner_address = 'Alice';
SELECT token_id, amount FROM token_ownership ORDER BY amount DESC;
SELECT owner_address, SUM(amount) AS total_amount FROM token_ownership GROUP BY owner_address;
SELECT * FROM token_transactions WHERE transaction_date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY transaction_date ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT sender_address, receiver_address, SUM(amount) AS total_amount FROM token_transactions GROUP BY sender_address, receiver_address HAVING total_amount > 1000;
SELECT * FROM token_ownership WHERE token_id = 100;
SELECT owner_address, block_timestamp FROM token_ownership WHERE owner_address = '0xABCDEF';
SELECT token_id, sender_address, receiver_address FROM token_transactions WHERE transaction_amount > 1000;
SELECT * FROM token_transactions WHERE transaction_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
SELECT owner_address, block_timestamp FROM token_ownership ORDER BY block_timestamp DESC;
SELECT token_id, owner_address, block_timestamp FROM token_ownership WHERE owner_address = '0x2a4e3b9d0FCEca8B5436a8366A0428aBFB28EeA3';
SELECT sender_address, receiver_address, transaction_amount FROM token_transactions WHERE transaction_amount > 1000;
SELECT * FROM token_ownership ORDER BY block_timestamp DESC;
SELECT token_id, owner_address, MAX(block_timestamp) AS last_block_timestamp FROM token_ownership GROUP BY token_id;
SELECT sender_address, receiver_address, SUM(transaction_amount) AS total_amount_transferred FROM token_transactions GROUP BY sender_address, receiver_address HAVING total_amount_transferred > 50000;
SELECT * FROM token_ownership ORDER BY owner_address DESC;
SELECT id, owner_address, amount_balance FROM token_ownership WHERE amount_balance > 100;
SELECT owner_address, SUM(amount_balance) AS total_balance FROM token_ownership GROUP BY owner_address;
SELECT token_id, amount FROM transactions WHERE from_address = '0x123abc' ORDER BY transaction_timestamp ASC;
SELECT distribution_id, distribution_amount, distribution_timestamp FROM governance_token_distribution WHERE distribution_amount > 500 ORDER BY distribution_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM token_ownership WHERE id = 1;
SELECT owner_address, amount_balance FROM token_ownership WHERE amount_balance > 1000 ORDER BY amount_balance DESC;
SELECT to_address, amount, transaction_timestamp FROM transactions WHERE token_id = 3 AND amount < 500 ORDER BY transaction_timestamp ASC;
SELECT token_id, SUM(distribution_amount) AS total_distribution FROM governance_token_distribution GROUP BY token_id;
SELECT owner_address, amount_balance FROM token_ownership WHERE amount_balance BETWEEN 500 AND 1000 ORDER BY owner_address ASC;
SELECT * FROM token_owners ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT address, balance FROM token_owners WHERE balance > 1000;
SELECT token_name, total_supply FROM governance_tokens ORDER BY token_name ASC;
SELECT id, from_address, amount FROM token_transactions WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT token_id, owner_id, timestamp FROM token_ownership_history WHERE token_id = 3;
SELECT id, address, balance FROM token_owners WHERE balance > 1000
SELECT id, from_address, to_address, amount FROM token_transactions ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT token_name, total_supply FROM governance_tokens WHERE total_supply < 100000 ORDER BY total_supply ASC
SELECT to_address, SUM(amount) AS total_received FROM token_transactions GROUP BY to_address HAVING total_received > 5000

SELECT th.timestamp, t.token_name, to.address AS owner_address FROM token_ownership_history th JOIN governance_tokens t ON th.token_id = t.id JOIN token_owners to ON th.owner_id = to.id ORDER BY th.timestamp DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM token_owners;
SELECT owner_id, owner_address, token_amount FROM token_owners ORDER BY token_amount DESC;
SELECT token_amount, owner_address FROM token_owners WHERE token_amount > 100;
SELECT owner_address, token_amount FROM token_owners WHERE owner_address LIKE '0x%' ORDER BY owner_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM token_history WHERE action = 'transfer' AND token_amount > 1000 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM token_owners WHERE token_amount > 1000 ORDER BY owner_id ASC;
SELECT owner_id, owner_address, SUM(token_amount) AS total_tokens FROM token_owners GROUP BY owner_id HAVING total_tokens > 5000 ORDER BY total_tokens DESC;
SELECT * FROM token_transactions WHERE sender_address = '0xABCDEF' AND receiver_address = '0x123456' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM token_history WHERE action = 'transfer' OR action = 'mint' ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 10;

SELECT owner_id, owner_address, TH.token_amount, GH.token_name FROM token_owners AS TO INNER JOIN token_history AS TH ON TO.owner_id = TH.owner_id INNER JOIN governance_tokens AS GH ON GH.token_id = TO.owner_id ORDER BY owner_id ASC;
